title: Flight Simulator 2020   Quiz 1st March 2021
description:
This is the 10thquiz on my channel. 
In this quiz there are no POI's close to the airport. The airport is on an island in the Caribbean and was a Dutch colony in the past. 
The question is: which airport am I departing from and which island am I flying above?

DISCLAIMER: you cannot win anything except the honor ;-)
